my daughter for a whole year now!

59
00:05:02,217 --> 00:05:03,952
Why haven't you arrested him?!

60
00:05:03,952 --> 00:05:07,722
We have increased the patrols
around your home.

61
00:05:07,722 --> 00:05:08,690
We just need a little more...

62
00:05:08,690 --> 00:05:12,026
How much proof do you think
I've handed over to you people?!

63
00:05:12,026 --> 00:05:16,397
And yet, you don't even know his name?!
What the hell is that about?!

64
00:05:16,397 --> 00:05:18,366
So, as I said...

65
00:05:18,366 --> 00:05:20,568
Hey, sorry for being late.

66
00:05:20,568 --> 00:05:22,837
Mr. Kisaragi, what's going on here?

67
00:05:22,837 --> 00:05:24,939
He showed up again yesterday!

68
00:05:24,939 --> 00:05:28,568
Yeah, I'm sorry.
We're doing the best we can...

69
00:05:30,745 --> 00:05:34,048
Akimoto, sorry, but could you
go buy me some coffee?

70
00:05:34,048 --> 00:05:34,883
What?

71
00:05:34,883 --> 00:05:38,019
I just got off the night shift
and I can barely keep my eyes open.

72
00:05:38,019 --> 00:05:39,486
I understand!

73
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:48,029
We've pretty much narrowed down
who the suspect is.

74
00:05:48,029 --> 00:05:49,797
What?

75
00:05:49,797 --> 00:05:53,568
I'm sorry it's taken so long.

76
00:05:53,568 --> 00:05:58,172
But in all honesty, the situation
calls for acting with prudence.

77
00:05:58,172 --> 00:05:59,469
Meaning?

78
00:06:09,984 --> 00:06:13,187
That detective?!

79
00:06:13,187 --> 00:06:15,890
