it'll all get covered up.

83
00:06:27,435 --> 00:06:30,505
So it was a detective...

84
00:06:30,505 --> 00:06:32,373
We will arrest him!

85
00:06:32,373 --> 00:06:37,679
But given this situation,
we must move carefully.

86
00:06:37,679 --> 00:06:41,749
Please have patience for just
a while longer until we have solid proof.

87
00:06:41,749 --> 00:06:45,420
But Mr. Kisaragi, my daughter
is at a breaking point!

88
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:47,752
-Any more and...
-Mr. Takamura!

89
00:06:49,657 --> 00:06:52,427
I understand.

90
00:06:52,427 --> 00:06:55,964
Please act like you know
none of this when Akimoto gets back.

91
00:06:55,964 --> 00:06:59,634
Avoid behaving oddly at all costs.
Do you understand?

92
00:06:59,634 --> 00:07:00,768
Yes.

93
00:07:00,768 --> 00:07:02,937
Sorry for the wait!

94
00:07:02,937 --> 00:07:04,005
Here you are, Captain.

95
00:07:04,005 --> 00:07:05,840
Your usual black was okay, right?

96
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,875
Yeah. Thank you, Akimoto.

97
00:07:07,875 --> 00:07:10,912
I put it on your tab.
You owe me three cups' worth now.

98
00:07:10,912 --> 00:07:12,937
Oh, sorry about that.

99
00:07:20,455 --> 00:07:23,157
Hurry up and come save me!

100
00:07:23,157 --> 00:07:24,317
"You have mail."

101
00:07:25,893 --> 00:07:27,554
"I love you,
Ryoko"

102
00:07:28,763 --> 00:07:29,764
