-Nooo!

105
00:07:37,972 --> 00:07:39,707
I'll pick you after school.

106
00:07:39,707 --> 00:07:41,676
Okay. Thanks, Dad.

107
00:07:41,676 --> 00:07:44,406
Don't worry. I'm with you.

108
00:07:45,513 --> 00:07:46,414
I'm sorry.

109
00:07:46,414 --> 00:07:49,417
Silly! There's nothing
for you to apologize for.

110
00:07:49,417 --> 00:07:50,577
Right.

111
00:07:52,086 --> 00:07:53,576
Takamura?

112
00:07:58,026 --> 00:08:01,596
You're Ryoko Takamura of Year 2,
Class A, right?

113
00:08:01,596 --> 00:08:02,730
Yes...

114
00:08:02,730 --> 00:08:04,866
Would you mind coming with me?

115
