118
00:08:11,973 --> 00:08:14,542
Here, go on in.

119
00:08:14,542 --> 00:08:16,711
Um...

120
00:08:16,711 --> 00:08:18,269
Come on.

121
00:08:19,447 --> 00:08:21,472
Oh, wait!

122
00:08:38,199 --> 00:08:39,928
You're here.

123
00:08:56,050 --> 00:08:57,185
You summoned me, remember?

124
00:08:57,185 --> 00:08:58,447
What?

125
00:09:00,388 --> 00:09:02,857
I am Ai Emma.

126
00:09:02,857 --> 00:09:04,525
Hell Girl?!

127
00:09:04,525 --> 00:09:07,028
Do you finally understand now?

128
00:09:07,028 --> 00:09:08,996
You came!

129
00:09:08,996 --> 00:09:10,164
Because you summoned me.

130
00:09:10,164 --> 00:09:11,699
Thank goodness!

131
00:09:11,699 --> 00:09:13,835
At last, it'll be over.

132
00:09:13,835 --> 00:09:18,101
Has this past year been that hard?

133
00:09:20,408 --> 00:09:22,944
It began with love letters.

134
00:09:22,944 --> 00:09:25,279
I found them in the mailbox every day.

135
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:29,317
And then they turned into weird gifts.

136
00:09:29,317 --> 00:09:30,579
Weird?

137
00:09:35,156 --> 00:09:36,390
That's fantastic.

138
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:38,392
He was trying to get your attention.

139
00:09:38,392 --> 00:09:41,362
It's pretty sick, though.

140
00:09:41,362 --> 00:09:42,852
And then?

141
00:09:44,499 --> 00:09:47,502
I started getting phone calls
and e-mails, too.

142
00:09:47,502 --> 00:09:50,471
I changed my e-mail address
many times, but it was no use.

143
00:09:50,471 --> 00:09:52,507
Quite the resourceful guy.

144
00:09:52,507 --> 00:09:56,544
After that, he would follow me
practically every day.

145
00:09:56,544 --> 00:09:59,147
And finally, I don't know how he got in,

146
00:09:59,147 --> 00:10:00,214
