will immediately be banished to Hell.

160
00:10:49,363 --> 00:10:50,698
To Hell?!

161
00:10:50,698 --> 00:10:51,933
However,

162
00:10:51,933 --> 00:10:53,734
once you have your retribution,

163
00:10:53,734 --> 00:10:57,705
you will have to pay the price
for it as well.

164
00:10:57,705 --> 00:10:59,240
Price?

165
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:02,710
Curses come home to roost.

166
00:11:02,710 --> 00:11:05,513
If you enter into the covenant,

167
00:11:05,513 --> 00:11:07,981
