280
00:22:08,976 --> 00:22:10,077
Later! Bye!

281
00:22:10,077 --> 00:22:11,078
Wanna drop by somewhere?

282
00:22:11,078 --> 00:22:13,478
Yeah, let's.

283
00:22:15,649 --> 00:22:17,851
Okay, as punishment,
the unsociable Ryoko

284
00:22:17,851 --> 00:22:21,421
must go explore the
haunted apartment building alone!

285
00:22:21,421 --> 00:22:23,223
What?! No way! I'm not going!

286
00:22:23,223 --> 00:22:24,391
Then, you can take us out to eat.

287
00:22:24,391 --> 00:22:25,759
I don't like that, either!

288
00:22:25,759 --> 00:22:28,353
-Picky, picky!
-Hah-hah!

289
00:22:30,464 --> 00:22:31,398
Well, I'll see you tomorrow!

290
00:22:31,398 --> 00:22:32,432
Okay, see you tomorrow!

291
00:22:32,432 --> 00:22:33,667
-Bye-bye!
-You owe us!

292
00:22:33,667 --> 00:22:34,861
Oh, please!

293
00:22:36,336 --> 00:22:38,238
You're late!

294
00:22:38,238 --> 00:22:39,573
Sorry about that.

295
00:22:39,573 --> 00:22:42,910
To make up for it, we'll go eat
wherever you want to today, Ryoko.

296
00:22:42,910 --> 00:22:45,811
Hey, that's a great idea, Dear.

297
00:22:50,817 --> 00:22:51,785
Hell...

298
00:22:51,785 --> 00:22:52,085
Hell...

